7.2.2 Fail-Safe Operation

Guaranteed safe operation under all conditions:

```
Safety mechanisms:
  • Watchdog timers: Automatic recovery from hangs
  • Power monitoring: Safe shutdown on power loss
  • Thermal management: Throttling to prevent overheating
  • Redundant computation: Critical calculations verified

Safety standards compliance:
  • Automotive: ISO 26262 ASIL-D
  • Medical: IEC 62304 Class C
  • Industrial: IEC 61508 SIL 3
  • Aerospace: DO-178C Level A
```

7.2.3 Ethical AI Framework

Responsible AI implementation:

```
Principles implemented:
  • Fairness: Bias detection and mitigation
  • Transparency: Explainable AI decisions
  • Accountability: Audit trail of all decisions
  • Privacy: Data minimization and protection

Implementation:
  • Bias monitoring: Continuous fairness assessment
  • Explanation generation: Human-understandable justifications
  • Consent management: User control over data usage
  • Impact assessment: Regular ethical reviews
```

